<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.7">
<l>vēṟāyā ṉirantēṉ vekuḷātuma ṉakkoḷentāy</l>
<l>āṟāven narakat taṭiyēṉaiyi ṭakkaruti</l>
<l>kūṟāvai varvantu kumaikkakkuṭi viṭṭavarai</l>
<l>tēṟātuṉ ṉaṭaintēṉ tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, who am [now] changed, beseech [you].</l>
<l rend="indent">Without angering, understand [this], Father:</l>
<l>When [my] five senses, coming one by one,  to vex [me],</l>
<l>Intending to cast me, [your] servant, into relentless, harsh hell,</l>
<l>Not trusting those who leave family [life], I take refuge in you,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
